{"tid":343307,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"李冰冰演中國虎影俠　變Marvel超級英雄亂入復仇者","createTime":"2017-08-01T10:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T11:19:41.000Z","uid":23707,"like":4,"dislike":79,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"378fa37310e8da947e219c74943794453e4d6bfb","tid":343307,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:38:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/電影/108760/李冰冰演中國虎影俠-變Marvel超級英雄亂入復仇者\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%2F108760%2F%E6%9D%8E%E5%86%B0%E5%86%B0%E6%BC%94%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%99%8E%E5%BD%B1%E4%BF%A0-%E8%AE%8AMarvel%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84%E4%BA%82%E5%85%A5%E5%BE%A9%E4%BB%87%E8%80%85&d=N9G3WaFchc9ulz0tyd%2BLikzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=b889634b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/電影/108760/李冰冰演中國虎影俠-變Marvel超級英雄亂入復仇者</a><br />\n<br />\nMarvel的超級英雄世界觀已成功打造為全球最大的生意之一，他們下個最睇好的巿場自然是中國，但作為非國產外語片要打入中國絕非易事，最好的例子就是《蜘蛛俠：強勢回歸》，香港都差不多落畫了，但要到9月才於內地上映。<br />\n<br />\n怎樣才賺到最多人民幣？當然不是拍多幾集《蜘蛛俠》，而是：和中國一起拍《蜘蛛俠》！Marvel深明這個道理，日前北京巿電影股份有限公司、北京新影聯影業股份有限公司和承興國際集團合資組成「聯承星影業」，將與Marvel之父Stan Lee合作，開拍一系列中國超級英雄電影，同場更宣佈其中5套Stan Lee創作的超級英雄片，包括《Alexa》、《圖像都巿》、《超人的叛變》、《紅色幽靈》和《無名小卒》，並邀得前Marvel全球巿場部副總裁Bob Sabouni擔任藝術顧問，他在記者會表示：「荷李活一直都嘗試將中國元素加入電影，但中國觀眾很聰明，一看就知道那些是強行植入；哪麼要怎樣創造一個中國的超級英雄？就是這個超級英雄真的是中國人。」<br />\n<br />\n消息指Marvel第一套進軍中國的超級英雄片其實已有定案，就是《虎影俠》（Realm of the Tiger），Marvel雖有「黑豹」也有「飛隼」，但就沒有老虎超級英雄，「虎影俠」更已敲定由李冰冰飾演，似乎是黑豹和黑寡婦的集合體，當然虎影俠也屬於MCU的一份子，未來絕對有機會在《復仇者聯盟》4、5、6、7集出場，還是會加入Defenders大戰鐵拳俠呢？"},{"pid":"d80d09984d528b84406a4dfb9db2d3d28605a79c","tid":343307,"uid":93986,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌<br />\n有預感會玩爛系列<br />\n好彩ironman,ca 唔再拍落去"},{"pid":"c98559e0d7d741ae7094c4d6f7fea83020247267","tid":343307,"uid":34123,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:42:22.000Z","msg":"fake news"},{"pid":"499a73e49f1cc2cf6eca87a521f0544ea5a2793a","tid":343307,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:53:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"994ea2a09f66a7aae4288d65398e6a833abffe23","tid":343307,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:55:54.000Z","msg":"Transformer 4 有版你睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d920920d606db13f21ecf7935cfd91fd70bfaa59","tid":343307,"uid":85946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T13:31:40.000Z","msg":"可唔可以拍還拍唔好入mcu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20d6960c526b3d723d7ab448d6afb183e50c0538","tid":343307,"uid":53705,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T14:18:41.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 <br />\nMarvel電影 近呢十年搵咁多錢, 但都要奶大陸 <br />\n洗唔洗呀<br />\n<br />\n你地唔奶大陸, 全世界都一樣咁多人去睇嫁啦(包括大陸人)<br />\n根本無必要搞臭自己個名呀<br />\n<br />\n當然, 你地可以話, 錢無人厭多"},{"pid":"2909cb78157dd968aa187eed0abf548f6c4ea7df","tid":343307,"uid":28256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T14:20:09.000Z","msg":"加入左一定搞到有柒味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d100ca9d930cb9a2ac68d6b936ed32119e57918c","tid":343307,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T14:22:55.000Z","msg":"舒化奶俠"},{"pid":"cb50710b50167681183707f0361fbe0c73873ad5","tid":343307,"uid":66934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T14:42:14.000Z","msg":"李冰冰